    "data": [
        [
            [
                ""
            ],
            [
                "Golly… If I had to endure one more date with someone crazy, I'd surely explode. "
            ],
            [
                "Nonetheless, I am still excited about finding a partner."
            ],
            [
                "This had been a dream I’ve had for quite some time ago,"
            ],
            [
                "and I was so, so close to fulfilling it that it seems like a waste giving up now."
            ],
            [
                "Especially knowing that by tonight, I’d finally have found the one for me."
            ],
            [
                "Still, being here is exhausting. I feel like I need to pee."
            ],
            [
                "I stand up, ready to give this dating event a break."
            ],
            [
                " A bell ring later,  a tall, scruffy person sits on my table."
            ],
            [
                "[He] didn’t seem to care that much about [his] appearance but still,"
            ],
            [
                "[he] had that something in [him] that interested me."
            ],
            [
                "Oh sorry, were you leaving?"
            ],
            [
                "I look at [his] nametag, ‘[Fabian]’, what a unique name."
            ],
            [
                "Wait, [Fabián]? Have I heard this name before?"
            ],
            [
                "There was something in this person that ringed within me, but I’m not quite sure why."
            ],
            [
                "No! not at all. I was just stretching."
            ],
            [
                "I quickly pretended to stretch and sat back down in a heartbeat."
            ],
            [
                " I hope my nervous smile doesn’t show that I’m trying not to have an accident here."
            ],
            [
                "Say, nice to meet ya. I’m [Fabián] and you?"
            ],
            [
                "My name is [tn]… as you can see on my nametag."
            ],
            [
                "[Fabián] looked intently at my nametag, just to pull away with a grin."
            ],
            [
                "Sorry, I can’t read."
            ],
            [
                "What? and… how did you register for this event?"
            ],
            [
                "C’mon, I’m pulling your leg. Of course I know how to read, duh!"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, makes sense after all."
            ],
            [
                "Still, I couldn’t help but feel the heat dwell up on my cheeks as I scold myself for believing [him]."
            ],
            [
                "Yeah… o-of course I knew, like- how could you not read? duh! haha!"
            ],
            [
                "I’m an idiot."
            ],
            [
                "I see how [Fabian]’s eyes light up as [he] looks at my phone case."
            ],
            [
                "Was [he] by any chance a connoisseur of good gaming titles?"
            ],
            [
                "Wait… Is that a Moki Moki writing club phone case?"
            ],
            [
                "Oh my, I love that game!"
            ],
            [
                "Yes, that’s it! I had never met any other fan before!"
            ],
            [
                "Although I see you’re very interested in gaming."
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, I am."
            ],
            [
                "Videogames are my escape, you know?"
            ],
            [
                "After studying hard and being bored all day"
            ],
            [
                "there’s nothing better than gaming for a while and just enjoying myself."
            ],
            [
                "These were great news."
            ],
            [
                "[He] likes videogames just as I do."
            ],
            [
                "Although, [he] better not be toxic when playing valofang."
            ],
            [
                "This is amazing! we should totally play together sometime!"
            ],
            [
                "My geekord nametag is-"
            ],
            [
                "And that stupid bell rings."
            ],
            [
                "I wanted to strangle the organizers for ruining this moment, "
            ],
            [
                "but then [Fabián] taps my shoulder and passes me a note as [he] gets up."
            ],
            [
                "My geekcord nametag is in there."
            ],
            [
                "I'll play any shooter or moba game with you if you'd like."
            ],
            [
                "I smile at Fabián as I see how they walk away."
            ],
            [
                "This event was going much better than what I had ever expected."
            ],
            [
                "Is Fabian a green or red flag?"
            ]
        ],
